OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781743669
OL,3,CGap between flat and house prices is
OL,4,Cwidest for at least 30 years, say
OL,5,Cexperts
OL,7,FThe average house costs 1.7 times the
OL,8,Fprice of a flat in the widest cash gap
OL,9,Fseen in at least 30 years, according
OL,10,Fto a property website.
OL,12,FZoopla said that the average price of
OL,13,Fa house has increased by 43% since
OL,14,F2016, while the typical value of flats
OL,15,Fhas seen a 10% uptick.
OL,17,FThe difference in the pace of the
OL,18,Fprice increases means the average
OL,19,Fhouse now costs 1.7 times the price of
OL,20,Fa typical flat, up from a multiple of
OL,21,F1.3 times a decade ago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
