CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781743669
OL,3,CGap between flat and house prices is
OL,4,Cwidest for at least 30 years, say
OL,5,Cexperts
OL,7,FThe growing gap could make life
OL,8,Ftougher for aspiring "second steppers"
OL,9,Fwho have previously bought a flat as
OL,10,Ftheir first home and are now looking
OL,11,Ffor a house in order to get more space.
OL,13,FBuyers can typically expect to pay
OL,14,F#327,000 for a house, #134,000 more
OL,15,Fthan the average price of a flat at
OL,16,F#193,000.
OL,26,@pD@VOUpD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
