OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781743669
OL,3,CGap between flat and house prices is
OL,4,Cwidest for at least 30 years, say
OL,5,Cexperts
OL,7,FZoopla said that, outside London, the
OL,8,Faverage gap is even wider ` a house
OL,9,Fnow typically costs 2.3 times the
OL,10,Fprice of a flat, up from 1.8 times in
OL,11,F2016.
OL,13,FBut in Scotland, the ratio has barely
OL,14,Fchanged in a decade. The average house
OL,15,Fthere is priced at 1.9 times that of a
OL,16,Fflat, which is similar to the 1.8
OL,17,Fmultiple seen in 2016.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
