FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781743669
OL,3,CGap between flat and house prices is
OL,4,Cwidest for at least 30 years, say
OL,5,Cexperts
OL,7,FLooking at England, the flat-house
OL,8,Fprice gap is widest in the Midlands
OL,9,Fand northern regions, where the
OL,10,Frelative affordability of a house
OL,11,Fmeans some first-time buyers skip
OL,12,Fflats entirely, Zoopla said.
OL,14,FIn the West Midlands, a house
OL,15,Ftypically costs 2.5 times a flat, the
OL,16,Fhighest ratio of any English region,
OL,17,Fit added.
OL,19,FZoopla used its house price index to
OL,20,Fmake the calculations and its records
OL,21,Fgo back 30 years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
