CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781743669
OL,3,CGap between flat and house prices is
OL,4,Cwidest for at least 30 years, say
OL,5,Cexperts
OL,7,FRichard Donnell, executive director at
OL,8,FZoopla, said: "Buyers who invest time
OL,9,Fto research and understand the system
OL,10,Fand get support can take advantage of
OL,11,Fthe gap between flat and house prices.
OL,13,F"A well-managed building with a long
OL,14,Flease and stable service charges is a
OL,15,Fvery different proposition from a
OL,16,Fproperty with less clarity on service
OL,17,Fcharges and a short lease."
OL,26,@pD@OOUuD@AOUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
