OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781743669
OL,3,CGap between flat and house prices is
OL,4,Cwidest for at least 30 years, say
OL,5,Cexperts
OL,7,FJen Lloyd, head of mortgage products
OL,8,Fand propositions at Skipton Building
OL,9,FSociety, said: "After years of saving
OL,10,Fa sizeable deposit, many buyers feel
OL,11,Fmore established and are purchasing
OL,12,Fwith longer-term plans already in mind
OL,13,F` thinking about a growing family or
OL,14,Fpets.
OL,16,F"They are choosing a home they can
OL,17,Ftruly settle into instead of a flat
OL,18,Fthat they anticipate outgrowing
OL,19,Fquickly."
OL,26,@qD@POUxD@AOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
