FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781743669
OL,3,CGap between flat and house prices is
OL,4,Cwidest for at least 30 years, say
OL,5,Cexperts
OL,7,FNathan Emerson, chief executive at
OL,8,Fproperty professionals' body
OL,9,FPropertymark, said: "Flats continue to
OL,10,Foffer an important and often more
OL,11,Faffordable route into homeownership,
OL,12,Fparticularly for first-time buyers.
OL,14,F"However, purchasers are increasingly
OL,15,Ffactoring in leasehold arrangements,
OL,16,Fservice charges, building safety
OL,17,Fconsiderations and other ongoing costs
OL,18,Fwhen making decisions.
OL,20,F"The contrast between Scotland and
OL,21,FEngland is particularly noteworthy.
OL,26,@qD@UOUvD@AOU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
