CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781743669
OL,3,CGap between flat and house prices is
OL,4,Cwidest for at least 30 years, say
OL,5,Cexperts
OL,7,F"The relative stability in Scotland
OL,8,Fsuggests that simpler ownership
OL,9,Fstructures can help support buyer
OL,10,Fconfidence and maintain demand for
OL,11,Fflats over the longer-term.
OL,13,F"These findings also highlight the
OL,14,Fsignificant regional differences that
OL,15,Fexist across the UK housing market.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
