CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781743669
OL,3,CGap between flat and house prices is
OL,4,Cwidest for at least 30 years, say
OL,5,Cexperts
OL,7,F"While affordability remains a
OL,8,Fchallenge in London and parts of
OL,9,Fsouthern England, many areas across
OL,10,Fthe Midlands, the North of England and
OL,11,FScotland continue to offer realistic
OL,12,Fopportunities for people looking to
OL,13,Fget onto the property ladder.
OL,15,F"Looking ahead, reforms designed to
OL,16,Fimprove transparency and simplify
OL,17,Fownership arrangements could help
OL,18,Fstrengthen confidence in the flats
OL,19,Fmarket and support greater housing
OL,20,Fmobility for future buyers."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU|D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
